name: Fade+ for Youtube
description:
Fade++ Remake that might be merged into this at some point.
Glass effect can be enabled with a Chrome flag: chrome://flags/#enable-experimental-web-platform-features
TamperMonkey (Theme + Old UI + Sidebar)
  • Code contributors:
    Agaigetsu
    Kronos
    Linuxcfg
additional_info:
Removed scrollbar when in fullscreen
Fixed theater/fullscreen having a top margin
Added glass effect on translucent elements. It uses backdrop-filter, that currently only works on Edge (April 2018 build) and Safari. It also works on Chrome by enabling a flag: chrome://flags/#enable-experimental-web-platform-features
